---
const { className = "", style = "" } = Astro.props;
---

<p class={`thumb-border-legend ${className}`.trim()} style={style}>
  Rainbow borders indicate published S-tier games. Gold borders indicate games with reviews.
  Pink borders indicate games with walkthroughs. Silver borders indicate completed player
  status. Blue borders indicate in_progress player status. Red borders indicate did_not_finish
  player status. Dark green borders indicate waiting_for_update player status.
</p>

<style>
  .thumb-border-legend{
    opacity:.75;
    margin:.5rem 0 1rem;
  }
</style>
